title: Looking for plat+Jungler
body:
We are a plat(all were diamond last year except support) team that participates in a weekly tournament. Players must be able to function in a team environment a.k.a. no flaming and no bashing other teammates. Players will need to have a fairly open schedule. Our current schedule is about 3 times a week no set day starting at 6:00 p.m. EST normally. If intrested add 
Blush uwu    in league 
or :Blush#9331 on discord !
